	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>You are all right, you are all wrong  ;), let me explain.<br><br> You MUST carry extra items in your bags, to get your AC/HP maxed for some fights, and get one or multiple resists as high as possible for other fights.<br> With out a doubt, Mana is important to a Cleric, so 200 Wis or as close as possible to it is best, but some situations will require you to go below 200 at times if you are going to have your other stats maximized for a specific encounter. Over or under 200 wiz is poor planing or a lack of equipment options in your bags, plain and simple.<br> AC/HP will rule for certain Melee only mobs, Resists are the ONLY thing that will keep you alive to heal others on other Mobs. It does not matter what your Wiz is or manna items are if you are dead from an AE DoT or AE DD.<br> Consider this, there is a Dragon in Veeshans Peak, that casts a 1500hp per tick AE DoT, it is best if you RESIST this dot, no amount of mana items AC/HP or Wiz will bail you out.<br><br>For those curios about a high end cleric, here is an example of my current stats and equipment at level 56 with all cleric buffs for that level applied ( notice the resists):<br><br>Hit Points: 2628 <br>Armor Class: 968 <br>Attack: 818 <br>STR STA AGI DEX WIS INT CHR <br>153 137 106 120 222  89 69 <br> <br>Poison Magic Disease Heat Cold <br>113     133    121    128 127 <br> <br>And my Current Equipment list:<br><br>Neck: Abalone Gorget ( KK ) / Yeldema`s Talisman ( WW ) <br><br>Face: Sarnak Hide Mask <br><br>Head: Etheral Mist <br><br>Left Ear: Yunnb`s Earing (VP - Phara Dar) <br>Right Ear: Abjurer`s Earing ( Hate Second Floor ) <br>Left Finger: Velium Diamond Wedding <br>Ring Right: Finger Velium Diamond Wedding Ring <br>Left Wrist: Velium Blue Diamond / Etheral Mist Bracer <br>Right Wrist: Velium Blue Diamond / Bracer of Stability <br>Arms: Etheral Mist / Donals / Vambraces of Stability <br>Hands: Gauntlets of the Black <br>Shoulders: Grim Pauldrons ( Named in TT ) <br>Chest: Donals ( Trakanon ) <br>Back: Brewers Mesh Cloak ( Innurok ) <br>Waist: Girdle of Diligent <br>Legs: Donals ( Venril Sither )/ Etheral Mist  <br>Feet: Royal Velium Frosted <br> <br> <br>Weapons <br>Primary Weapon: Water Sprinkler of Nem Ankh ( Epic ) <br>Offhand Weapon: Shield Shield of Elders (VP - Pahara Dar) / Prismatic Shi <br>Range: Medicine Totem / Thex Mallet <br> <br> <br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
