	   <tr><td colspan=2>Let me clarify something... at the end game your stats don't mean @#%^. His higher wisdom makes him a better cleric. Period. You fight anything past level 40 and i don't care if you have a High Elf stamina or a Dwarf stamina... as a cleric your HP multiple is too small for your to survive.<br><br>While it may be true on the low end of the game pre-30 you have a huge edge, and soloing pre-30 ditto, on the high end WISDOM IS GOD. The quicker you get it to 200, the quicker you soft cap, and the fewer items you need to do that (because of your higher inate wis) the more item spots open for +mana items.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
